    "Package StructureThe implemented environments in this work are Python classes that inherit from the OpenAI Gym base class gymEnv and follow the same conventions regarding required class methods.",
    "This is because certain RL algorithm frameworks include a method for checking that the inputs and outputs of the environment are compatible with the agents.",
